snippet.title: Trinity Linton
snippet.description:
Hi, my name is Trinity and I am so happy you are joining me on this adventure. I take you along and show you how to preserve food, garden, and cook! I have been canning for 6 years now and pressure canning for 4 years. I love being able to preserve my own foods and I hope you get something out of this channel!
Join me for Gardening, cooking, canning and a lot more! 

If your interested in purchasing through Azure, using my link helps me out and blesses us! Thanks for your support! 
https://www.azurestandard.com/start
